Text: Introductory MeetingWith the recent changes in the EC organization I am interested in exploring other opportunities within the Wholesale group I would greatly appreciate the opportunity to introduce myself to you and to get any suggestions you might have in this regard Attached for your information is a copy of my resume If you have a few moments this week please let me know Thank you Peter
